style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;随着特朗普的贸易战争&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/FfYr9UbNTu0O-JFyMWpgmYYc2JILGKhAHhxkEyv5fS2kZ2tmUNJ19j9VfdWi3zmhcC4PyhvPZRk6u9487ivPpFZXKRHOq4vXxhVQ7PyJx5dF_ApWM8W7BJqSgddy2V5gCkt8bprBr3aB3dJhT9wQjfsXY7gqmaN3-x3THTRFtliGRhr3m1yEIEzK00_ehIdK-ChAOc-anikZvVX_VMVsRkQ66D7qoYilNqp6niKWbjkSRgLDS-OyXF3ShPF8Lsc75XQFhjf6l2ZxOpjqWtBTefa58e19yYdSNvZ89VbuvHXwzSpVIt2erJrMFp32bw2YczNCJwN6P3DSRDxvbj_DPvCS3WDbPfcJFXBUSnyZnB-vDb-0Gwex7IF3HRI/iKw1zBM0VMIJ-HP7vTbQwuNJdgUfVTOy/7" target="_blank"&gt;将刀具变成一个已经努力实现今年的交易市场&lt;/a&gt;，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;价值数十亿美元的收购&lt;/strong&gt;和首次公开募股被搁置。据说，票务平台StubHub Holdings，Fintech巨头Klarna Bank和Trading Platforing Group都在计划中的列表中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/i7jl0n2YuRTdQgqUMDFpN7qR58i2dHrGFig4SxOZ-8i-vY0luieFijwvgH6D3ORa4zwyChMHhClJ7BT5gPyJO8vRH2K1Ep9bVvUleagv-33B8as3lmh-Td3fgJofmrg1MlaG7e0ijNYILU-RShbcERSk5qFN-Ve3ixmniuxXztbR0pdVi0VpU3fjotf1yxmi9gWUZ4Ds3FgwY077hpA35hnEvzFa0msan1_i3hBg_BOUmg4nPnQqI6RSJ9IJnUGs8WqXI6N5rEw8qpqSUX3AlR1yF2VP3tP4v1p5XdyQ-5fpY5xwd6KyRWRK4-DkeDZGB2h_iiaIppxMjjAtZ1rYOc-RivoNNELG0P5BVBeuRplYFb9kKiotdVeAaFI/CDVUP87YaJLOoTyDpCfAcDz5_8Yh0C0x/7" target="_blank"&gt;停下来&lt;/a&gt;。 Adtech Group MNTN和保险公司Ategrity Specialty Holdings的列表也被搁置。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;彭博新闻周五&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3S1xYMaEObObLCJVgJPjV_O1blqmUv5NaGOTmjpupsa6Sty8KP3GCmpRdl0Kcr8renJuttLwjAwKwzuket8PdqdmoUmreWJ9hqCb5UvhG59CzQZNy58HZ17xZsMF5EJp5dqft97euTaWFK9dQjzwnF_LRpTYviytrOX3AmvE8EroaTHtgx-R46rwsdCKyFI9Md4RdoXnI94E5Mwd29J7I-o-2areAA9s63AjVatOOzoCiVdXHiIMVdAxfrDV-MvvjEb22nS1YbtcQ7BfzqKjmfJAKnUXKmTZOQz7LaJHgKSYvz2QrXChjP0_YxKSCUvSF0JzJyT60XL_cJQHs7GLSNg4w7Sqf6TtmCoDAG6RhpDwlfGQdEvINlU4ixg/Q44OwFpdDLDQ06UxMUu3LgXHI5nQjAxG/7" target="_blank"&gt;报道&lt;/a&gt;说，法国建筑材料生产商Cie。DeSaint-Gobain决定推迟出售其自动玻璃单元，该单元的价格可能高达25亿欧元（28亿美元）。私募股权公司KKR＆Co。已&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/x-_JtU5C_ZHmDkRm1KpEkIKzFpKgD2ueVYkFB6K5O2e_lMUm9beGqMtrP8Z3nkvB-ENLpRroJQUT-JcBW3temDKRLcuc84jHL0qN-tMrVH9nlX39b3XRd0yMZ5is8CWb4IyqKJXmKgIdFwJQi3a4_PFKEKvXIO3AegJ0FwpuLQb3agPNreuLPorPZK3LtUKGsm2XpwA6K1wUaLj6Z-7nhNfvRWEG53tauXhEW6Pxay8qkX5WobSVDaL86XbjTmDFWQRdRvOZ0ZjGEroIjdpc7GTyDldzTrjukrx3ZfsksEEfms83OoSorChASL9RRRENaOVXP0jVWExp_v6Vg-piD-QIITE7UBQ6MiTXhgEUgrVwIW37ecFlK-9NS1s/khE8klJiegtQTjz99IizLqRDb2q2-16r/7" target="_blank"&gt;离开&lt;/a&gt;了一个财团，讨论了对毒品和化妆品包装制造商Gerresheimer AG的收购，该公司的市场估值约为20亿欧元。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;随着投资者和分析师评估特朗普关税的后果&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;，对欧洲中央银行利率削减的期望&lt;/strong&gt;正在上升，得出的结论是，通货膨胀的结果将更加良性。然而，增长会受到影响。这位78岁的特朗普在白宫&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/cudYAOssDkM8suz--99btH2VWQsLYKoScHAIAFvD7020eTt1cH3aNY9Xzkz3sakVizgafQCunH4q7aqnnyEBC7HDh7RD6TRJNSN7QPWqTHJtEmfjDdtZrwZMl64xFASf84PiB627Ne4BDorzvCaiahs2-WgUUJU6eRJ7ch6jkyLMGNCJ_KFY0T28EEzNTlTNJsFyTIwyprvd8hrmKSPPVTARxdpLDdLFkFlHUG_TX8Un-LXwfq2VRgHgVsNvsI2vLv6yClB3I2bN6cjOZCe6Eomc87JlXRyVKu5zEHkG4oHsWTSFCJsZHzbTtJOrpG1Hw9crdplgPGEM38LCPEuwcHUPucN9uXRnxhDzcF4ZcXl8S6bi5gM5Jz0QtWY/YEQpUKH6IgSr_JAL9Lxasjl4e9TBJfhw/7" target="_blank"&gt;透露的78岁的特朗普关税&lt;/a&gt;两天后，今年的欧元区借贷成本至少降低了3次，这是从之前的两项降低。经济学家越来越确定&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/K93xNOFDPmHDZuVsQdlqdFQVpxQIn-2WdWqZCumIf19ZivCwVAMQVsVPC6xqMh9JiIuoGTRcuBIR37yeJ34YlQLyqZ_4N1c4lWRTnKR76_VGY-K8W3MfTcaoX0zuMFcxrO5ibysKHrUczW44tGgET9ojyBgcYG0bOqBvDOnLQKII3B4_BSKDrA6AWOF32U73DWlEJWJgXocq_yJbjMfVwOqh28UAG3cPCT8auBPLt-iF8KgPD4nR69xaGhQCLJdr8jwlpmWFOcjxB0-aIffLgfKM-eY0F-xtjq_40KQFl2cf_KGtmUMHuqOpNIxkNQ6943ze4uHPU417VD7FRNA7KBIty43DNGx6lN1Mln-KmZpu_Fjga3IEaADQvCs/DBQ1mz582JZ7ky9vw_g1QNO9lbNGwI6A/7" target="_blank"&gt;欧洲央行将在4月做出其中的第一步&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;转变背后的观点是，特朗普的征税范围要高于刺激消费者的价格。彭博经济学在中期期间看到欧盟产量的约1％，这对通货膨胀施加了下降压力。同时，美元继续反抗通常的预测，即它将加强并&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HvntclaxPvPS68ruz54C2ytLXkpqhMMeMuz4sAo4duPVBkAN0eMTQLlW-BV61a4WTK6axsb5SLIgh4zz3gJ4fMxxnccDzryzkEjXIDvM6efaVekO7GHNLKJKAAoViLBqaY69R4oX4FBAEYywLw_z2bq9WBWTgGomWTmx1NChFrOZHOLOMCz-W6gwszn0-oKGMN3bDQ5MzFWedsORerA7Au7dShESMgIk9kwzKZ3e-R_Os38t3HtfJRJ5SdMD7HcYDy6PfzczBgxkfa0_TXrGw_tZ1t6kuD4qe8VyjUD7_bqxARIpUuBDl50oEVDWjOWQoWT7glSqbpeY9yYSNMOyFI7wUfDmosgPDxnzIGUEMVJdARXGiLO4f2vejj4/QJLqsQ89YA0raCzQi7PGKnLsTdxvkAyX/7" target="_blank"&gt;做出相反的情况&lt;/a&gt;- 阻碍了人们担心较软的欧元会增加进口成本。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zWN4peYJeEiKxSvUbpiEN4NRNNIefBhli8RMPqxTuyehPrVeVTPsG8cx_aMIkmV8l74hqabcTyyCD-D7HqRwgPdprOySDVgI9Ohv9BYTfjKTiKOpNVDWNVchloOkoQt3Rf7NUxx7OeAtiZnrONvygk6LZ3aZkNHQJFSlU1LRGgsNDs6RiOo2i70M7CMdvikJSFVUXH-OjCPryfu77HSa6uggUqxd8kShKgkSjtxPq4SPZDblyBqwfFaualH4ugFcW3GSmNskgnKKiIK1ZXDOxn6sUNjprDXsiLVOqm-FNOvhYN4FT96B29NBYZCq5E2K5F4t0-adKzOEyftelkS-l4tV8KFo4KQgGcxD93jGwY21ilcsfScM4HJcT8A/V4Q1tvIc3nIap8CIysgriyoe1qPt3Pkm/7"