-ozempic-drugs-fda.html"&gt;·&lt;/a&gt;肯尼迪（Robert F. Kennedy Jr. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-radius: 8px; padding-bottom: 18px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/PlAz7asOngWByjOCQO6JTKOfNq-T8aF68K8GxkwgT25heEbgksC4ge5XNgq7hguDw31eUDiw0NRemNTcu4sGGC64953AbL-YrmUk0CN1QFIgbIQBYHJPgfHzD6hsrF-G28HVw4mxk2OiF1I2JoI0GE37b3QKW-gj49v74YcTX70aMZU1hLKMGyLoNt8FCUBem2Cxe46PiYnH8b7u6IK-khWnOvkt93GdgkYh-CyqBXj1Pmk4w7tzSJgLpnNq2dyIUJmDAiMtxHZq7FflMsuJP9h9ERYH8aS3KzHZ6DJui1pGx9O0oqgym9ncZHm-lZeMzrMPPJSA_myIzQ4pXnGEob7NTexjT3Qm-QatZdSU54r3QXnUBo99nG10oNY/yjedvkiurDW85mys3xHdA1oWbymuRMFs/7" rel="nofollow" style="color: #000000; text-decoration: none; display: block;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1Zk7xsavenU/v1/550x381.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img class="email-ssl-image" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1Zk7xsavenU/v1/550x381.jpg" style="border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; width: 550px; height: 381px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TjtWso5dc1JDDJkXJeOrNPCN4D10eGDDBUfbZ0t3PHpydNgIP6XJ0pYqBILO7NrZ--cdosaN91MvXWsOBVzSwHpRR2plj8