t;报复。万斯&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Vtq1XhfEjCNPBtVyVOlzRlc2ejFVyGuYkW88g-c2gvlZaVkRbbKMqPqnK1n2x7YINXAc531EEugElnpp-FJMsv1OMnR9V24lwCQiAhpF5Qx3mdI9INQTqRjlo4nO08BZXSA83XKWqd-86xB1oUJAPocmuvOxHCTf7nWKJIy3S6iJUhPp-41CPggNOPoplKgFU4h8vNhQe_9MT49MWFrJQAqOonzwNJyO8EEaq23M21erKI0IqAJXDk9U4WI3NbaO8_DRrA9k_uX6z8cOwr96zdKCiOBhRgLJqfEntzbF6b2GEbz97BIxRaTKI--jRBj98sWlazrlJ4-zwL5VU47kw09LhIoGgERXvCGVyglwLgsFsiyd0HHP6ZyEEpg/slAaVPi22HaRwFjA0CI40XsqzB93I-kR/7" title="淡化了市场的行动"&gt;淡化了市场的转变，&lt;/a&gt;因为临时疼痛。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）敦促全球最大的贸易集团欧洲联盟的企业&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nTt76Wu8iyMjgH1Mt8MjGAqwgvIU8U7RtvIlxwv0gEMvOS8KITgc-CQemlCMsXmAIEiLzwS2AVgYuGJgpgZpAtQqd8gJ-CqGcClGhdLjwXcMH2zslxYMhypH48NGqoGgnJ2V6KZyjGM9MmjUw2aOIPwUV05xb9dIAooNYIbbGtLpe-V4uKrjgFF6AciArX8uwV70AQKwyVLFpMbWkiJpfg0B8Ep1KaLnDv7B5yo33yo9zm3tikEWq0-MO6twZ1Vk3Yxh-yArgTcsDDkG9NVryDAB_6Ih3LfYqnV6iBST5GVjLe1vZq-MxwKJqpJS-e9DfIsp4bCBl927sVc3_-L1l9A2x6GSH1c1VHF9UL8-fkRI6QdAmBBQfvn4rJw/qMEM3GJ2HQkr6Vuwt0qHdgCrvUYOOY6J/7"&gt;停止在美国支出&lt;/a&gt;，而日本总理希格鲁·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）则在与反对派领导人的罕见会议之前宣布“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mnaJwyFi6FbeSTWJqg5v-8f5deURPsm0ZqDkaxWgvirMsTsnABLLrrYeJhFRD1mEieFKAW6YSgWFI7dMLx6IOy3pxb_xaj7Vd4_UMZ-Dia7En26Pnm-r0TuN-5IRFiSaKu7tjhohsBnbRr54f-cry02U9UeZ__NxQNtvJ2AOAsS92uMOy_0ZK--PIxA5AecxwRo5yn4LcWTGTZcoVdCg8D7uczq8xC1JTqwDy5zr5RhZ8l7nGqaPbZBu5l1eusyqkBUL4nlKMzNoUo0Hc7uUXwKs2XA4nRKhuXHMC1h1byodpIE6_WG_Zhm10vVqhJVNvcg2UuIsGkGBHFbPO9gu297VfJE2g-iGdKezFadXCGicMSMtHqnbEbXdglM/WjuJn_BAUgPCijxFmMW7mQdaZwG9mLuE/7"&gt;国家危机&lt;/a&gt;”，讨论统一的回应。特朗普建议，如果其他国家能够提供“惊人的”，但他还标有更多征税，他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/2quWMp5CeE4p1KAeJSbYQ3ZCfkpKy4UoR72QqxdX08v49kVNcflSqFpOAVdocZ0TJ-XSlROX3H-TkMWLILKoL5B2k4L5eJUQQIpf2RnQxEH4FGw46qz9LlWi_i5sylsquHbQPc4kc-IowGRa4TxOMfWL0z8uVuNzFMSxlhKWDWCk-G2k6p-mD4Fjcxs4YuzSBHD6FhpkZZWxqfTt0R6MPVlKvbm_MndUCf7vsyBZejMYPFioEblY_kbfAckY9XcKngbddBhchPvUUL5h5zTzBv2-0MHaI5WxbTjoBsJ2MM9-6PTylG6lJ-LeQNvZcyU6N4k-ZuF_KZ-A_hfyKRKwWWkaINTK0G85TYKAq7NVB7oWddmmHyCo_Mg-kyM/-hQsclpK9xw7TC302crOAwXprafQjfYS/7"&gt;可能会在路上提出&lt;/a&gt;更多的征税，并提到半导体和药品。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icNa_WNGir3o/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icNa_WNGir3o/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;韩国法院&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Oy-EOuEeqU9Qb0CFO8MTmpjxerAwy6Eco9SH1wfDa5orXFz8G4vu0PQ2c7qwIQjLB7gzFVUH4MBqP2mENPM5pWr2qeTLQp5kB7piwd6Lk_G_PcRbNa892JbN4hkvXBzpVx36aBRmVGEtKFC86j4_NMk5GAHcVDinA7FlYejvKEH-Vbi-OAMZ1c0n3IjZG8Emye54_JqxeQihH6zfLnMDoPwx58Y--iECq9UZwgGnRwbE2Vv1RKHZ9L8fxdRh3WtXsMZXC8TO2bp4ryWTKE6QfBsTuHu1klmCDkZd1KeccglVixcT6Wx0NERvghH32R4hFpBFms-JHmcoYCzmigp7RQ21vMM9GbP0Gwut6qhfVXdS3rzzJZq7_brkwns/ChKfJYa97uSJpmgBp1bN0oCbN7ZSxRdT/7"&gt;在12月的&lt;/a&gt;短暂戒严宣言中将总统Yoon Suk Yeol撤职，为总统竞选铺平了道路，以结束已经抓住全国数月的领导层面的真空。宪法法院&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/FgPkwox_-RjhKJCuopsugG-uwpmUiX-rJaYsNRuONcZ8pJw2L3PoV__uRUza-TYk5nLmNhFjNHEpXA1I3T1G_kueMRulsTtbvhYlDs1GlHxGOLH8kRKLIFy0PIQOx2GKmSZn1bTVJ6kXwPfe_Yp07wO3i6nWP3IM6_oDJ3